        "timestamp": "2019-07-31 14:16:02.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAs we discussed in scrum call, I'll replace the hardcoded ip by shell variables passing into the script. At the moment, I'll keep all the scripts there and also add a README file saying these scripts will be used only when test is planned to run on component-wide deployment. Otherwise, in OOM deployment, no need to run the scripts. \n\nThe stability test was triggered before lab upgrade is done. SO, I still use those scripts to deploy containers in 2 VMs. I can try to run again the test using the latest lab deployment and update the wiki too.",
        "patchset_number": 1
